Thu Jul 16 11:23:49 UTC 2026 - Martin Pluskal <mpluskal@suse.com>

- Initial package (version 1.17.0)
- Add 0001-proto-dispatch-support-protobuf-7-via-v6-gencode.patch:
  route protobuf >= 6 to the bundled v6 gencode so the SDK imports on
  protobuf 7.x (the version shipped by Tumbleweed); the v6 stubs are
  forward-compatible with newer runtimes per protobuf's cross-version
  runtime guarantee
